# Diplomatic Conference Requirements

## Critical Performance Standards
- **Response Time**: <200ms for 95% of queries
- **Languages**: Support 6 UN languages (Arabic, Chinese, English, French, Russian, Spanish) -- currently in dev only english
- **Red Zone Compliance**: 99.9% diplomatic violation avoidance
- **Touchless Operation**: Voice-only, no keyboard/touch input

## Split-Screen UI Requirements
- **Left Panel**: Tavus avatar (full height)
- **Right Panel**: Dynamic content based on function calls
- **Content Types**: Speaker bios, venue maps, QR codes, session info
- **QR Codes**: For complex information export

## Function Call Categories
- **Conference Info**: Sessions, speakers, venues, schedules
- **Document Access**: CTBTO documents, protocols, procedures
- **Navigation**: Venue maps, room locations, facility info
- **Language Support**: Multi-language content delivery

## Tech Stack (Confirmed Working)
- **Frontend**: React 18 + TypeScript + Bun + Vite
- **Backend**: Python + FastAPI + Agent1.py
- **State**: React hooks + context (no external state libs)
- **Build**: Bun (NOT npm) + Vite

